<section class="notice">
  <div class="step mono">// known limitations</div>
  <h2>What we know — and don't.</h2>
  <p>Traffic analysis defense is a young research area. A poorly designed defense can leak as much as no defense at all, and we'll continue learning about what works as more people deploy. Dodge is engineered to be safe-by-default: with a well-thought-out defense, your traffic should be no easier to identify than without one — usually much harder.</p>
  <p>We publish our research, source code, and limitations openly. If you're a content provider thinking about deployment, <a href="/contribute">we'd like to help</a>.</p>
</section>

